definitions.definition: A sudden , involuntary contraction of a muscle , a group of muscles, or a hollow organ .
examples: Jessica went into spasms after eating a peanut.

definitions.definition: A violent , excruciating seizure of pain .
A sudden and temporary burst of energy , activity , or emotion .
